    "The family of deep learning approaches to program repair develops and applies deep learning techniques to identify software defects and generate patches [542].",
    "Deep learning models have been widely applied to repair a wide range of program errors.",
    "We divide existing work into three categories, including compilation error repair, runtime error repair, and specific domain error repair.",
    "Compilation error repairA compilation error is an error that can be detected during compilation.",
    "Programs with compilation errors fail in program compilation or linking; meanwhile, programs with compilation errors cannot be directly handled by program analysis tools [543][544][545].Compilation errors prevent source code from being transformed into executable machine code during compilation."
  ],
